e.','The kitchen understands that I am cooking  because the stove is on and need to see well, so it turns on all the lights. '),(1900,10,225,'The lights come on very dim when I enter the restroom','I need to use the restroom in the middle of the nigh','Because the home knows what time it is, it turns on the lights very low so I don\'t wake up too much when I use the restroom and can go right back to sleep. '),(1901,9,225,'Only the flood lights should turn on But all the lights in my home turn on','There is a strong storm going on outside my home','There is a glitch or something that made my home think that the storm is an intruder. I would have to reset something on the main panel to turn off the lights. '),(1902,8,225,'My Home sense that the door is trying to be forced open','Someone is trying to break into my home','All the lights in the house come on. This may deter the intruder. '),(1903,7,151,'If a person stand still or sit without a movement.','It should not only sense the movement it should also sense the presence of the person in a room using body temperature.','Light should turn off only after that person left from the room'),(1904,8,151,'a person approaching to a room from another room the sensor should detect the direction of the person to which room he is heading to','Sensor should measure the speed of the movement of the person and detect the direction of the person ','The light should turn on before he leave the adjacent room'),(1905,10,151,'at the night time','reading book in the night time','should increase the brightness according to the nature of work'),(1906,9,151,'Should sense the area of movement and direction','If an unauthorised person approaches externally towards the home','lights should turn on inorder show the presence of security'),(1907,8,151,'the light is off before he enters into the room','an unauthorised person enters into the room ','light should stay off even if he enters the room or blink according to the discreation of the user f